details.Application Process: The application process includes registration, filling of application online, payment of fees, and final submission.
details.Eligibility Criteria: The eligibility criteria include age limits, educational qualifications, and reservation categories.
details.Exam Format: The exam format includes multiple-choice questions in Kannada language.

details.Eligible Candidates: Candidates of Karnataka origin passed the qualifying examination in the college located in Karnataka state willing to take admission may fill the application form online on the KEA Website http://kea.kar.nic.in from 29-11-2024 to 02-12-2024.
details.Contact Information: Phone: 080 - 23 564 583 Helpline : 080 - 23 460 460. e-mail : keauthority-ka@nic.in Website : http://kea.kar.nic.in
